data.description: This 2001 home sits under beautiful shade trees on .68 acres. This home features 4 large bedrooms with walk-in closets and 2 full bathrooms. The primary bathroom has dual sinks and a separate shower/tub. This home also has a wood burning fireplace, a large laundry room and a shed outside to store all your outdoor equipment. Enjoy the privacy of the large backyard and cool off in the above ground swimming pool. Bring the family, this home has everything you need!  The roof was replaced in 2021 and the septic tanks were pumped in 2022.
